data.description: Welcome to 1461 Arden in Las Vegas, NV 89104! NO HOA!!! This affordable new listing won’t last long. Buyer can take advantage of the existing solar agreement for eco-friendly living and lower energy costs. The open floor plan fills the interior with natural light, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. The spacious private backyard is a rare find, perfect for outdoor gatherings and relaxation. The listing agent has the solar agreement details for your convenience. Enjoy easy access to amenities while maintaining a peaceful lifestyle. Don’t miss out on this opportunity – schedule a showing today before it’s gone!
